PropertyTypeDescriptiondecimalPlacesnumber｜nullMaximum number of decimal places to include in output. Default value to 2.fixedDecimalsboolean｜nullWhether to always display the maximum number of decimal places. Default value to falsethousandsSeparatorstring｜nullExample of values: &#039; &#039;, &#039;,&#039; and .… Default value to &#039;&#039;.unitstring｜nullThe unit in which the result will be returned (B/KB/MB/GB/TB). Default value to &#039;&#039; (which means auto detect).unitSeparatorstring｜nullSeparator to use between number and unit. Default value to &#039;&#039;.
